```python
            else:
                turn = _pd_turn(bbox_cx, frame_center)
                turn = int(turn * TURN_LEFT_SIGN) if turn <= 0 else int(turn * TURN_RIGHT_SIGN)
                last_approach_speed = APPROACH_SPEED_CLOSE
