## Phase 5 — Reliability Enhancements (P2/P3, NEW)

> Additional improvements beyond the original diagnosis to make autonomy significantly more reliable.

---

### Change 5.1 — Improved search pattern (sweep instead of jerk)

**Problem:** Current search alternates direction every 1.2 s, causing jerky left-right-left behavior. Robot may miss objects between sweep arcs.

#### [MODIFY] [ecosweep_manual_final_patched.py](file:///d:/Robot_newcontrol/hardware/pi/ecosweep_manual_final_patched.py)

**Find** (the SEARCH_TURN_DURATION_S constant):
```python
SEARCH_TURN_DURATION_S = 1.2
```

**Replace with:**
```python
SEARCH_TURN_DURATION_S = 2.5    # Longer sweeps to cover more area (was 1.2)
SEARCH_FORWARD_BURST_S = 0.5    # ← NEW: drive forward briefly between sweeps
SEARCH_FORWARD_SPEED = 40       # ← NEW: slow forward during burst
```

**Find** (the SEARCH state, around line 325–346):
```python
