## Summary of All Constants Changed

| Constant | Old Value | New Value | Reason |
|----------|-----------|-----------|--------|
| `DETECTION_LOSS_GRACE_S` | 0.2 | 0.6 | Survive missed YOLO frames |
| `PROPORTIONAL_GAIN` | 0.5 | 0.85 | Stronger steering |
| `CENTER_DEADZONE_PX` | 15 | 12 | Tighter precision |
| `PICKUP_STABLE_FRAMES` | 5 | 3 | Trigger pickup more reliably |
| `PICKUP_ARM_DOWN_S` | 0.5 | 1.0 | Reach ground |
| `PICKUP_GRIP_CLOSE_S` | 1.8 | 2.0 | Firmer grip |
| `PICKUP_ARM_UP_S` | 0.6 | 1.0 | Fully raise |
| `PICKUP_CREEP_DURATION_S` | 0.4 | 0.3 | Slightly less creep |
| `SEARCH_TURN_DURATION_S` | 1.2 | 2.5 | Wider sweeps |
| *New:* `EMA_ALPHA` | — | 0.4 | Detection smoothing |
| *New:* `DERIVATIVE_GAIN` | — | 0.15 | Oscillation damping |
| *New:* `TURN_ONLY_THRESHOLD_PX` | — | 50 | Stop-turn-go |
| *New:* `PICKUP_COOLDOWN_S` | — | 2.0 | Avoid re-targeting |
| *New:* `SEARCH_FORWARD_BURST_S` | — | 0.5 | Move between sweeps |

